This script will backup a MongoDB Replica Set

Script input parameters: 

# Database name or all
MONGO_DBS="$1"

# Mongo host name
MONGO_HOST="$2"

# Mongo port
MONGO_PORT="$3"

# Mongo Collection
MONGO_COL="$4"

# Backup server name, it is optional parameter if you leave "" then it will take backup in same server
BACKUP_SERVER="$5"
